description.en:
What is the project about?
A memecoin on Solana so fly and so fresh that you'll want to scoop that dip!

What makes your project unique?
Stealth launch memecoin on Solana with 94% of tokens initially fully locked liquidity

History of your project.
Stealth launched on May 3rd at $4k MC and currently sitting at $200k+ MC

What’s next for your project?
Expansion of exchange venues and creating a fresh meme driven experience on Solana

What can your token be used for?
It's a memecoin. It;s used for entertainment!
